T1  - The anatomy of an informal financial market: Rosca participation in Taiwan
AU  - Levenson, Alec R.
AU  - Besley, Timothy
JO  - Journal of Development Economics
VL  - 51
IS  - 1
SP  - 45
EP  - 68
PY  - 1996
DA  - 1996/10/01/
